  "title": "🦅 Sales & Marketing Representatives – No Experience Needed❗️",
  "description": "<p><strong>Ready to kickstart your career in Sales &amp; Marketing❓</strong></p>\n<p>We’re on the hunt for energetic, outgoing individuals who are hungry to learn, love talking to people, and want to be part of a vibrant team that works hard and has a blast doing it. No experience? No problem—we’ll give you the tools, training, and support to thrive.🔨</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>☺️ What We Offer:</strong></p>\n<p>• 💰<strong>Commission-Based Pay:</strong> Unlimited earning potential – you control your income!</p>\n<p>• ✈️<strong>Travel Opportunities:</strong> Explore new cities and expand your network on the go.</p>\n<p>• 🤠<strong>A Fun, Supportive Environment:</strong> Think team nights, challenges, incentives, and a squad that feels like family.</p>\n<p>• 👏🏻<strong>Personal Development:</strong> Learn the art of persuasion, communication, and leadership.</p>\n<p>• 🏅<strong>Flexible Growth Path:</strong> Move up fast based on your effort and performance.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>💪🏻 You’ll Be Doing:</strong></p>\n<p>• ✅Promoting products and services face-to-face or at events</p>\n<p>• ☑️Engaging with customers and creating lasting impressions</p>\n<p>• ✅Representing brands with enthusiasm and confidence</p>\n<p>• ☑️Collaborating with teammates and crushing team goals</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>👀 You’ll Fit Right In If You:</strong></p>\n<p>• 🤓Are you a people person who thrives in social settings</p>\n<p>• 👊🏻Are you motivated, ambitious, and ready to learn</p>\n<p>• 💯Want more than just a “job” – you’re after growth and fun</p>\n<p>• 🌠Are open to travel and new experiences</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>📌 Singaporean/PR only</strong></p>\n<p><strong>📄No resume? No stress.</strong></p>\n<p>We care more about your energy and attitude than your background.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>‼️Apply now and let’s start the adventure‼️</p>",
